## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Orchestration:** [n8n](https://n8n.io) (self-hosted / cloud)
- **Messaging Layer:** Telegram Bot API
- **AI Models:**
  - Google Gemini (Chat Model)
  - Groq (Chat Model)
  - OpenRouter (Chat Model — multi-provider access)
- **Tools / Integrations:** Gmail (read messages)
- **Memory:** n8n Simple Memory
- **Post-processing:** JavaScript (Code node)

