## 💬 Example Usage

| You type… | Routes to… | What happens |
|---|---|---|
| `force build me a landing page outline` | **Ai Force → Team Force** | Generates a structured landing-page plan |
| `nexus connect my email and summarize today's leads` | **Ai Nexus → Team Nexus** | Pulls Gmail, structures lead data |
| `victor analyze this campaign report` | **Ai Victor** | Fast analytical breakdown |
| `team brainstorm 5 ad angles` | **Team agents** | Multi-step reasoning |
| *anything else* | **Ai Default** | Fallback agent with Gmail access |

